  "readme_html": "\n        \n          <p><img src=\"/assets/library/lfm2.5-thinking/0f3b101a-f2ef-4a5c-a0bb-a8edecac35e3\" alt=\"image.png\"/></p>\n\n<p>LFM2.5 is a new family of hybrid models designed for on-device deployment. It builds on the LFM2 architecture with extended pre-training and reinforcement learning.</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>On-device personal assistant</strong>: Designed to power real-life applications, chaining tool calls, and following complex instructions on all devices.</li>\n<li><strong>Compressed performance</strong>: Competitive with much larger dense and MoE models on instruction following and agentic tasks.</li>\n<li><strong>Unmatched throughput</strong>: Fastest in its size class on both CPU and GPU inference</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><img src=\"/assets/library/lfm2.5/2eecda91-5cc6-4212-9382-25e05b6e68ad\" alt=\"benchmark\"/></p>\n\n        \n      ",
